column5: If we were countin dimes this weekend we would have had a few bucks thats for sure.  That said, I think I lost a few bucks too...freshly minted dimes are crazy!   Good fishin boys, see ya next weekend
Nice picture!!!!
Nice chromer!

Nice job Kemp, spectacular picture and catch.  MTBF
Picture credits go to Silvio....I just caught the fish.  "Dude, jam your reel into the weeds"
